{"tid":2217342,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"被譽為「Jennie 和 Tiffany 綜合體」：實力比臉蛋更出色，她被看好成為下一位大勢女歌手","createTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T14:05:43.000Z","uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5168bd62333eeb00d112849029ee180d2b4c9c","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:04.000Z","msg":"說到大勢女偶像，絕對少不了女團成員 Jennie，獨特的「貓相」和一出場就令人著迷的舞台氣勢，在一片漂亮可愛的女偶像中突圍而出，連續多個月蟬聯女團評價前三名。身為資深 粉絲，也在心裡默默期待，是否會有第二個能媲美 Jennie 的女偶像出現？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.adaymag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/e9130f73fbbdbdf8cfdd1191361f4bfc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fe9130f73fbbdbdf8cfdd1191361f4bfc.jpg&h=6324c8ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1667fa96a4923af5aaf07cd4eb32aa6a8b1fe25b","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:14.000Z","msg":"近日，一名被網友認為「神似 Jennie」女歌手 msftz（미스피츠）在網路上引起關注。兩人都是眼尾上揚的大鳳眼，臉蛋小巧、強烈的個人氣質，的確第一眼看起來和 Jennie 有幾分相似。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.adaymag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/dab46cd2e5c63fbd48a05411f21b059c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2Fdab46cd2e5c63fbd48a05411f21b059c.jpg&h=fb92e98f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"563d31832d22a3dafb49511990f6dc3816c0fb89","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:28.000Z","msg":"也有網友說 msftz 還帶有一點少女時代成員 Tiffany 的神韻，和 Jennie 相比更有稜角的臉型、略帶無辜的眼神，真的有點 Tiffany 的影子。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.adaymag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/54ff6612766a09f25295ba5064f6cba4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F54ff6612766a09f25295ba5064f6cba4.jpg&h=641771f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"307d216a1573c600fe30e4e3f842141e52953a1d","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"除了Jennie 和 Tiffany，還像這位大勢女歌手<br />\n<br />\n而 msftz 微嘟的嘴唇、立體的下巴稜線，則是讓我第一眼想到同樣也是大勢的 Solo 女歌手請夏。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.adaymag.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/85c1778b3e4bdc048bd7a0f1cacc4bf2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adaymag.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F85c1778b3e4bdc048bd7a0f1cacc4bf2.jpg&h=a0499490&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d70a0703ef0323b1675b1de4beebd38c0e9ee200","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:00:59.000Z","msg":"出道前就因出色的音樂實力擁有人氣<br />\n<br />\n她，絕不只是明星臉而已<br />\n<br />\n不論像誰，每個都是人氣頂尖的樂壇女星，而 msftz 可不只有明星臉而已，1997 年出生的她，今年 23 歲，不以一般多人團體的方式出道，而是獨立推出自己的音樂作品，擅長輕快、爵士曲風，聲線慵懶、音色甜美，歌唱實力不容小覷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDne582p8kR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDne582p8kR&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=eb55c66c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDne582p8kR&h=32204947\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CDne582p8kR</a>"},{"pid":"ccacdaeea2df678878c8f6c8bc5d92ab52e497aa","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:01:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CDYdzPFJ3b6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDYdzPFJ3b6&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3c443fb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCDYdzPFJ3b6&h=ec8fa10d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CDYdzPFJ3b6</a>"},{"pid":"b40de560830aae14df574058d6044f5bcfac91c7","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:01:27.000Z","msg":"出道前，就在音樂平台《SoundCloud》上，以 치킨（韓文的 Chicken，因為她喜歡吃炸雞）為名，推出許多自創歌曲，獲得超過 140 萬的瀏覽紀錄，有一定的知名度。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CBNq3lapxN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNq3lapxN0&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=5d10167f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNq3lapxN0&h=fa84fba3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CBNq3lapxN0</a>"},{"pid":"c3485589695b048f3e8cdb1a5194724dc7eccddc","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:01:50.000Z","msg":"今年一月以《Eternity》正式出道，專輯裡的《2080》和 msftz 親自參與作詞作曲的《환상 Fantasy》都很好聽，《Bye Bye I Finally Disappear from Your Life》也很推薦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bAQpVphG3ko\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbAQpVphG3ko&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=72fb2b3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bAQpVphG3ko</a><br />\n<br />\n七月推出的歌曲《Tell me about your world》，清純唱腔與溫和旋律，讓人一聽上癮，是很適合秋天窩在被窩裡聆聽的歌曲。"},{"pid":"9d4e2556fe744f162805ac19ba6ae08469a9b324","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:02:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nBsibROVB7A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnBsibROVB7A&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzhZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=70e4b150\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nBsibROVB7A</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然出道不久，距離走紅還有一段路，但這個兼具外貌與實力的她，絕對很有機會成為下一個抒情路線的大勢女歌手，如果你也喜歡爵士曲風的歌曲，那一定不能錯過這位寶藏女孩的作品。"},{"pid":"2c14fdd38b1f55874b59a8e0ff3163eda723fccb","tid":2217342,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:24:25.000Z","msg":"@bitch <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/12/133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F12%2F133619_7cf305542df037e5a2654c1c8a16ade9.gif&h=25438751&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid"